OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780916574
OL,3,CTeen who delayed exams elected to
OL,4,Cnational Parliament
OL,6,FGabriel Raimondo has become one of the
OL,7,Fworld's youngest politicians.
OL,9,FThe teenager had to delay his A-Levels
OL,10,Fin order to focus on his Jersey
OL,11,FElection campaign - and only reached
OL,12,Fthe minimum qualifying age for
OL,13,Fcandidates ten days ahead of polling.
OL,15,FThe 18-year-old's 1,603 votes were
OL,16,Fenough to claim third place in the St
OL,17,FBrelade district election, granting
OL,18,Fhim a place in the island's Parliament.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
