PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780916574
OL,3,CTeen who delayed exams elected to
OL,4,Cnational Parliament
OL,6,FHe could not match the numbers posted
OL,7,Fby experienced politician Jonathan
OL,8,FRenouf, who topped the parish poll
OL,9,Fwith 2,414 votes, and Montfort Tadier
OL,10,Fwho finished with 2,122 in second.
OL,12,FHowever, the landmark result sees him
OL,13,Fbecome one of 28 Deputies elected to
OL,14,Fthe Jersey States Assembly for the
OL,15,Fnext four years.
OL,17,FHere, he will make decisions that
OL,18,Faffect the around 100,000 people who
OL,19,Flive in the self-governing Crown
OL,20,FDependency.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
