OL,3,CTeen who delayed exams elected to
OL,4,Cnational Parliament
OL,6,FUnlike Westminster, Jersey's
OL,7,FParliament is mainly made up of
OL,8,Findependents - although Gabriel aligns
OL,9,Fhimself with the new political
OL,10,Fmovement Value Jersey, which says it
OL,11,Faims to make the island more
OL,12,Faffordable.
